title: Peta E‑Dagang Malaysia
subStitle: Penyenaraian E‑Dagang Yang Paling Popular di Malaysia
monthlyVisitsContent: Lawatan purata laman web bulanan antara April 2017-Jun 2017
appInstallSources: Jumlah minimum muat turun applikasi menurut Google Play (Total worldwide downloads)
contentEmployees: Sumber: LinkedIn. Data akan dipaparkan sebagai (n/a) jika bilangan pekerja tidak dipaparkan
contentMerchants: E-dagang yang menerima lebih daripada 100,000 pengunjung setiap bulan atau 100,000 pengikut media sosial layak untuk senarai ini. Industri-industri berikut tidak termasuk dalam senarai ini: e-tiket, perkhidmatan kewangan, perkhidmatan sewa, insurans, perkhidmatan penghantaran, makanan & minuman, meta-carian, kupon dan laman web cashback. Semua e-dagang yang memulakan perniagaan mereka sebagai kedai fizikal tidak termasuk dalam senarai ini.

title: The Map of E‑Commerce Malaysia
monthlyVisitsContent: Average monthly website visits between April 2017-June 2017
appInstallSources: Minimum number of App installs as per Google Play (Total worldwide downloads)
contentEmployees: Source: LinkedIn. Data will be displayed as (n/a) if the number of employees are not available
contentMerchants: E‑commerce who received more than 100,000 visitors per-month or 100,000 social media followers are qualified for this list. The following industries were not included in this list: e-ticketing, financial services, rental services, insurance, delivery service, food & beverage, meta-search, couponing and cashback websites. All e-commerce who initiated their business as a physical store are not included in this list.
